      • inflate

        public final void inflate(@NotNull
                          @NotNull Class<HALMenu> menuClass,
                          Payload payload)
        Adds a new menu to the current tree and displays it. This does not create a new tree, and instead adds on to the existing tree.
        Parameters:
        menuClass - The class of the menu to add to the new tree and display. Must have a constructor that takes only a payload.
        payload - The payload to run the menu with.
        Throws:
        HALGUIException - Throws this exception if there is a problem creating a new menu from the given class and payload.
        See Also:
        HALMenu, Payload
